{"tid":2169196,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"提禁堂食 羅致光：落雨先知咁多戶外工人","createTime":"2020-08-22T10:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T14:14:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fc8c0b16dfd822dde080dc9fa38b1790d4400222","tid":2169196,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:03:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/N7RJIZCPFNEK7G4DUKQ3XZY464/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FN7RJIZCPFNEK7G4DUKQ3XZY464%2F&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6eTimN4xbKJd0qqIWjmG9ok%3D&h=de611207\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FN7RJIZCPFNEK7G4DUKQ3XZY464%2F&h=1f103246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/N7RJIZCPFNEK7G4DUKQ3XZY464/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n提禁堂食 羅致光：落雨先知咁多戶外工人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kMTqPaxgoi-STT36UukSeNfRXyg=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EANNHXEHT5EDVOA66BM5KEKATI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkMTqPaxgoi-STT36UukSeNfRXyg%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEANNHXEHT5EDVOA66BM5KEKATI.jpg&h=4c427b3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■羅致光受訪時稱，推行禁堂食前從未考慮過戶外工作者。港台片段截圖<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】每年炎夏，勞工處都會提醒戶外工作人士小心中暑，小學常識教科書也會列舉建築工人、清潔工人在戶外辛勞工作。但智商高達160的勞工及福利局局長羅致光接受港台節目訪問時說，早前政府全面禁止堂食，事前沒人提及戶外工作人士，直至實施當日下大雨，「大家就知道，原來有咁多」。他承認有責任，但不內疚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認有責任但不內疚<br />\n<br />\n羅致光接受港台節目《鏗鏘說》專訪，表示禁堂食措施實施前兩、三星期，從來沒考慮過也沒有人提及，在戶外工作人士及清潔工人等是最受損害一群，「所以咪覺得就咁囉」。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，對於過去一年多的社會狀況，羅致光稱跟很多香港人一樣，「就係唔開心囉」，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情惡化，政府上月29日起全面禁止食肆堂食，大批打工仔要在公園、路邊甚至跪在地上用膳，全城怨聲載道，。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"3e0ce965a56fef207e48eebb400c0e774e016ef8","tid":2169196,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:33:34.000Z","msg":"晉惠帝d fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b1bef42b555798d9cceb8f603f4eb8f5faf61a8","tid":2169196,"uid":15605,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:22:03.000Z","msg":"係人都知羅致光弱智"},{"pid":"a82133082fec38505bc6407c9f098d5e7079d2d0","tid":2169196,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:37:19.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲"},{"pid":"b0cfae922b634811d30f8f9e83aa12a1ab557a34","tid":2169196,"uid":320680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0b1bef42b555798d9cceb8f603f4eb8f5faf61a8","tid":2169196,"uid":15605,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:22:03.000Z","msg":"係人都知羅致光弱智"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:39:17.000Z","msg":"人地 IQ 160<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b907c9956142fcdda250234e125be3c8e5f3da2e","tid":2169196,"uid":49247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:40:15.000Z","msg":"國之將亡"},{"pid":"4ac8c651d822e25c1d499ee16b6a35d0ca73b769","tid":2169196,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:41:55.000Z","msg":"咁多個特首好似得曾蔭權係推銷員出身，最貼地"},{"pid":"08ac90a3c90709d5a49cd11f2e3d070e9c06ef1b","tid":2169196,"uid":20809,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:57:52.000Z","msg":"咁既垃圾拎三十幾萬一個月，搞d政策出黎俾人當笑話咁笑下，大家開開心心就咁日復日<br />\n<br />\n我都想做件咁既垃圾俾公眾屌下笑下，我袋20萬一個月就ok,政策保證好笑過佢"},{"pid":"82295937b2a3171ae1084728999f7166551f72a9","tid":2169196,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4ac8c651d822e25c1d499ee16b6a35d0ca73b769","tid":2169196,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:4